Extended fork modifications by Timon Hargesheimer include:

New Files:
- src/formatters/git.ts (Git export formatter)
- src/lib/git/repositoryManager.ts (Git repository management)
- src/lib/git/anonymizer.ts (Anonymization utilities)
- test/formatters/git.spec.ts (Git formatter tests)
- test/lib/anonymizer.spec.ts (Anonymization tests)
- .env.example (Environment variable documentation)

Modified Files:
- src/formatters/console.ts (Added anonymization support)
- src/formatters/csv.ts (Added anonymization support)
- src/formatters/json.ts (Added anonymization support)
- src/formatters/index.ts (Added git formatter export)
- src/formatters/types.ts (Updated formatter interface)
- src/cli/parser.ts (Added --anonymize and --format git options)
- src/cli/types.ts (Added anonymize option)
- src/cli/io/output.ts (Added git format handling)
- src/cli/commands/report.ts (Added anonymize parameter)
- src/cli/commands/allCommits.ts (Added anonymize parameter)
- src/types.ts (Added anonymize to FormatterOptions)
- package.json (Added simple-git dependency, updated metadata)
- README.md (Added git export and anonymization documentation)
- .gitignore (Added git export output patterns)
